VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT didReceive\s+challenge|NSURLSessionAuthChallengeDisposition\.useCredential
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SecTrustEvaluate|SecPolicyCreateSSL|pinnedCertificates|ServerTrustManager && MISSING:test|development|localhost
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects custom TLS challenge handling that may weaken certificate validation.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Certificate Validation Override.
